According to the Independent, Mr Powell was arrested after detectives were called to his home on Thursday.

Detective Inspector Andy Maxfield from Staffordshire Police said: 'At this stage of the investigation we are not looking for anyone else in connection with this incident.'

Police were called to the scene at around 8pm on Thursday. 

